item.title: Pilot
item.description: It’s been a few months since I wanted to start a programming blog, mainly because I want to write about how I struggle with dumb stuff and how I solve it, if so. To be honest now I feel lazy about writing but I feel like I’m in debt. I’ve been saved lots of times by strange programmers in the Internet who decided to magnificently contribute to the whole humanity, by posting their solutions.
